'''{{ConjecNameAU|Kahhori}}''' is a [[human]] known as '''{{Conjecture|Apocalypse}}'''.

==Biography==
When a [[Kahhori|Variant]] of Apocalypse was attacked by [[Eminence]], [[Incarnate]], and [[Executioner (Watcher)|Executioner]], they attempted to erase all versions of them from existence. [[Captain Carter/Super Soldier Peggy Carter|Captain Carter]] stopped the trio, allowing for Apocalypse to continue existing.{{Ref|WI308}}

==Trivia==
*In the comics, '''En Sabah Nur''' is a villainous [[mutant]] known as Apocalypse who is a frequent foe of the [[X-Men]].
*[[Oscar Isaac]] portrayed Apocalypse in ''{{WPS|X-Men: Apocalypse}}''.

